typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		veisubgruoid as string,
		veisubgrunome as string,
		veisubgrudescricao as string,
		veisubgrudt_inclusao as string,
		veisubgrudt_alteracao as string,
		veisubgrudt_exclusao as string,
		veisubgruveigruoid as string,
		veisubgruusuoid_inclusao as string,
		veisubgruusuoid_alteracao as string,
		veisubgruusuoid_exclusao as string,
		veisubgrupousoid as string,
		veisubgruautomotor as string,
		veisubgrupafroid as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	wildcardPaths:['sub_grupo_veiculo']) ~> GetVehicleSubGroup
GetVehicleSubGroup select(mapColumn(
		veisubgruoid,
		veisubgrunome,
		veisubgrudt_inclusao,
		veisubgrudt_alteracao,
		veisubgrudt_exclusao,
		veisubgrupafroid
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RemoveColumnsVehicleSubGroup
RemoveColumnsVehicleSubGroup sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SaveStVehicleSubGroup
